Package data.math.definitions

Interface Relation<X,Y>

Type Parameters:
X - the type of the domain.
Y - the type of the codomain.
All Known Subinterfaces:
Function<X,Y>, TransitionFunction
public interface Relation<X,Y>
An interface for a binary Relation R subset of X x Y.
